    "date": "2008-09-19T16:13:28Z",
    "text": "Back on Track Act - Amends the Railroad Revitalization and Regulatory Reform Act of 1976 to revise interest rate and credit risk premium requirements for direct loans and loan guarantees for construction or repair of railroad bridges located in disaster areas due to flooding beginning in 2008. Extends the term of repayment of direct loans or loan guarantees from 25 years to 35 years."
